account%20or%20a%20debit%20card%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20about%2060%25%20of%20their%20total%20spending.%20The%20analysis%20didn't%20track%20how%20the%20participants%20spent%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20GBI%20pilots%20study%20changes%20in%20participants'%20happiness%20and%20mental%20health%2C%20those%20findings%20don't%20specifically%20include%20how%20the%20extra%20things%20people%20purchased%20for%20themselves%20or%20their%20loved%20ones%20made%20them%20feel.%20To%20analyze%20quality%20of%20life%20impact%2C%20experts%20often%20look%20at%20individual%20anecdotes%20and%20qualitative%20findings%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20quantitative%20spending%20data%20on%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20of%20the%20parents%20BI%20spoke%20with%2C%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20meant%20affording%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-parents-afford-childcare-get-stable-jobs-gbi-ubi-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estable%20day%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20stroller%20to%20go%20on%20neighborhood%20walks.%20Others%20told%20BI%20they%20used%20the%20cash%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-mothers-afford-maternity-leave-baby-supplies-ubi-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20a%20new%20crib%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20onesies%20for%20their%20newborn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaint-paul-minnesota-basic-income-pilot-500-stipend-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMelvin%20Carter%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20member%20of%20the%20advocacy%20network%20Mayors%20for%20a%20Guaranteed%20Income%2C%20said%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20fully%20capture%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20improvements%20in%20a%20dataset%20because%20the%20benefits%20differ%20widely%20between%20participants.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20clear%20that%20cash%20aid%20has%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20parents%20have