0f7f27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20iStock%3B%20Natalie%20Ammari%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Wannapa%20Suprasert%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20from%20Thailand%20now%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco%20who%20was%20scammed%20out%20of%20over%20%24300%2C000.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20thought%20that%20I'd%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20drawn-out%20scam.%20I%20always%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-all-savings-changed-retirement-plan-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escams%20were%20about%20making%20quick%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20someone%20calling%20and%20asking%20for%20%242%2C000%20within%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20went%20through%20three%20months%20of%20psychological%20warfare.%20The%20scammers%20created%20a%20new%20reality%20for%20me%2C%20making%20me%20think%20that%20if%20I%20didn't%20comply%2C%20I%20could%20be%20jailed%20or%20deported.%20They%20framed%20themselves%20as%20the%20good%20guys%20who%20could%20help%20me%2C%20never%20rushed%20me%20to%20do%20anything%2C%20sent%20me%20fake%20documents%2C%20and%20even%20talked%20to%20me%20on%20the%20phone%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20register%20in%20my%20brain%20that%20the%20scammers%20would%20invest%20so%20much%20time%20and%20energy%20into%20this.%20Now%20I%20know%20that%20they're%20professionals%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThey%20said%20I%20was%20a%20suspect%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20scheme%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20Friday%20afternoon%20in%20March%20when%20I%20got%20the%20call%20that%20changed%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20my%20data%20analyst%20job%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgovernment-impostor-scams-prey-on-fear-during-pandemic-bbb-study-finds-1029446957%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaller%20said%20she%20was%20from%20the%20Thai%20embassy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20She%20asked%20to%20speak%20with%20Wannapa%20Suprasert%2C%20which%20spooked%20me%20because%20I%20generally%20go%20by%20my%20nickname%2C%20Bow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20me%20that%20someone%20had%20smuggled%20a%20passport%20bearing%20my%20name%20into%20the%20Bangkok%20airport.%20She%20started%20interrogating%20me%20on%20whether%20I%20had%20lost%20or%20sold%20my%20passport.%20I%20was%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20her%20that%20I%20hadn't%20lost%20my%20passport%20and%20offered%20to%20prove%20I%20still%20had%20it.%20She%20said%20she'd%20transfer%20me%20to%20the%20Thai%20police%20to%20file%20a%20report.%20My%20call%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolice%26quot%3B%20dropped%20a%20couple%20of%20times%2C%20and%20someone%20posing%20as%20an%20officer%20asked%20me%20to%20add%20them%20on%20LINE%2C%20a%20messaging%20application%20popular%20in%20many%20Asian%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20didn't%20strike%20me%20as%20fishy%20because%20I'd%20just%20gone%20back%20to%20Thailand%20in%20February%20and%20communicated%20with%20the%20Thai%20consulate%20via%20LINE%20about%20renewing%20my%20passport%20while%20I%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20after%20my%20call%20had%20dropped%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20phone%20the%20Thai%20embassy%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20but%20nobody%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20officer%26quot%3B%20claimed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Central%20Investigation%20Bureau%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20Thai%20police.%20He%20sent%20me%20a%20PDF%20copy%20of%20a%20police%20report%20he%20said%20he%20had%20filed%20for%20me.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20discovered%20my%20identification%20number%20on%20a%20list%20of%20at%20least%20239%20people%20involved%20with%20an%20international%20money%20laundering%20scheme.%20I%20was%20now%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20had%20to%20send%20updates%20four%20times%20a%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fake%20officer%20sent%20me%20a%20PDF%20with%20the%20alleged%20photos%2C%20names%2C%20and%20descriptions%20of%20five%20masterminds%20behind%20the%20fictional%20laundering%20scheme%20and%20interrogated%20me%20over%20video%20chat%20about%20whether%20I%20knew%20any%20of%20them.%20The%20supposed%20masterminds%20included%20two%20bank%20managers%2C%20an%20American%20police%20officer%2C%20a%20Thai%20consulate%20official%2C%20and%20a%20Thai%20exchange%20student%20in%20the%20US.%20After%20I%20told%20him%20I%20didn't%20know%20any%20of%20them%2C%20he%20said%20that%20they'd%20investigate%20and%20help%20me%20clear%20my%20name.%20But%20because%20I%20was%20a%20suspect%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20send%20daily%20updates%20about%20my%20whereabouts%20and%20activities%20to%20ensure%20I%20didn't%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20send%20three%20pictures%20of%20myself%2C%20my%20location%2C%20and%20a%20description%20of%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20four%20times%20a%20day%3A%20at%209%20a.m.%2C%2012%20p.m.%2C%205%20p.m.%2C%20and%208%20p.m.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20if%20I%20didn't%20comply%2C%20he%20would%20send%20agents%20to%20monitor%20me.%20If%20I%20tried%20to%20escape%20or%20missed%20a%20daily%20report%2C%20my%20family%20could%20be%20jailed%20and%20their%20assets%20frozen%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20also%20said%20I%20couldn't%20tell%20anyone%20because%20it%20might%20interfere%20with%20the%20investigation%2C%20which%20also%20involved%20the%20FBI.%20If%20I%20did%2C%20I%20risked%20jail%20time%20and%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scammers%20played%20on%20my%20fears.%20I%20had%20worked%20so%20hard%20for%20a%20better%20education%20and%20life%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-immigration-needs-reform-losing-workers-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimmigrating%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20was%20afraid%20of%20being%20deported%20and%20losing%20my%20status.%20The%20scammers%20also%20warned%20of%20people%20who%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20supposed%20crime%20syndicate.%20Leaving%20my%20apartment%20to%20go%20to%20work%20or%20shop%20for%20groceries%20was%20suddenly%20frightening.%20I%20thought%20someone%20was%20really%20after%20me%20and%20that%20at%20any%20moment%2C%20anything%20could%20go%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20many%20moments%20when%20I%20was%20skeptical.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20into%20the%20scam%2C%20I%20received%20a%20LINE%20message%20from%20the%20Thai%20Consulate%20in%20LA%20warning%20about%20scammers%20impersonating%20the%20Thai%20police.%20But%20the%20scammers%20convinced%20me%20that%20the%20warning%20message%20had%20been%20sent%20by%20the%20criminals%20to%20keep%20me%20from%20complying%20with%20the%20investigation.%20Because%20of%20the%20threats%2C%20paranoia%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20sleep%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20believing%20every%20word%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20sent%20the%20scammers%20%2481%2C000%20in%20a%20wire%20transfer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwire-fraud%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewire%20transfer%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20on%20April%203%2C%2011%20days%20after%20the%20initial%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scammers%20said%20I%20was%20accused%20of%20selling%20my%20bank%20account%20to%20the%20crime%20syndicate%2C%20so%20in%20order%20to%20clear%20my%20name%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20investigate%20the%20money%20in%20my%20bank%20account.%20They%20claimed%20to%20have%20a%20contract%20with%20Hong%20Kong%20police%20who%20specialized%20in%20investigating%20money%20laundering%2C%20so%20I%20wired%20%2481%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20pretty%20much%20all%20of%20my%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20bank%20account.%20They%20left%20me%20with%20some%20money%20for%20day-to-day%20spending%20and%20paying%20rent%20and%20said%20they%20would%20eventually%20return%20the%20full%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20the%20fake%20police%20officer%20told%20me%20that%20my%20money%20cleared%2C%20but%20the%20court%20would%20need%20to%20examine%20all%20of%20the%20evidence%20as%20well.%20He%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20travel%20to%20Thailand%20to%20appear%20in%20court%2C%20but%20warned%20that%20someone%20had%20been%20killed%20making%20the%20same%20trip%20to%20clear%20their%20name.%20He%20said%20I%20could%20also%20ask%20someone%20else%20to%20appear%20on%20my%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20I%20couldn't%20risk%20telling%20my%20family%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20officer%20if%20he%20would%20represent%20me%20in%20court.%20He%20played%20it%20very%20well%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20to%20ask%20and%20that%20he%20needed%20a%20few%20days%20to%20decide.%20He%20agreed%20the%20next%20day%20but%20said%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20send%20money%20for%20collateral%20to%20ensure%20I%20didn't%20escape%20while%20he%20was%20representing%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThen%2C%20I%20transferred%20another%20%24150%2C000%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20any%20more%20money%20since%20I'd%20already%20emptied%20my%20life's%20savings.%20I%20lied%20to%20my%20family%20and%20asked%20them%20for%20money%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20I%20was%20applying%20for%20a%20Ph.D.%20%E2%80%94%20which%20had%20been%20my%20dream%20%E2%80%94%20and%20needed%20to%20show%20the%20school%20that%20I%20had%20%24200%2C000%20in%20my%20bank%20account%20to%20help%20with%20my%20chances%20of%20being%20accepted.%20My%20family%20valued%20education%20so%20much%20that%20I%20knew%20they%20would%20send%20me%20that%20amount%20without%20many%20questions.%20They%20wired%20the%20money%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20it%20from%20my%20aunt's%20retirement%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20wired%20%24150%2C000%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolice%26quot%3B%20in%20two%20chunks%2C%20first%20%24100%2C000%20and%20then%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20from%20Bank%20of%20America's%20fraud%20department%20called%20me%20after%20I%20made%20the%20%24100%2C000%20transaction.%20She%20asked%20me%20what%20the%20money%20was%20for%20and%20informed%20me%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcrypto-crime-pig-butchering-scam-bitcoing-trafficking-fraud-cryptocurrency-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bpig%20butchering%26quot%3B%20investment%20scams%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fromance-scammer-peter-gray-tinder-fraud-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eromance%20scams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Neither%20of%20those%20applied%20to%20me%2C%20so%20it%20didn't%20occur%20to%20me%20that%20I%20was%20being%20scammed.%20I%20lied%20and%20said%20that%20the%20money%20was%20for%20my%20sick%20cousin%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20whom%20I'd%20never%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwells-fargo-customer-lost-68k-after-being-tricked-scammer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etried%20to%20wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20additional%20%2450%2C000%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later%2C%20the%20bank's%20fraud%20department%20called%20again%2C%20asking%20more%20questions%20about%20where%20the%20%24100%2C000%20came%20from%20and%20where%20it%20went.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20my%20dad%20had%20meant%20to%20send%20it%20to%20my%20cousin%20but%20accidentally%20wired%20it%20to%20me.%20They%20told%20me%20to%20show%20up%20at%20the%20local%20branch%2C%20where%20I%20found%20out%20that%20the%20%2450%2C000%20transfer%20had%20been%20canceled.%20The%20scammers%20instructed%20me%20to%20appear%20agitated%20and%20say%20that%20my%20cousin%20needed%20the%20money%20for%20brain%20surgery.%20The%20%2450%2C000%20transfer%20was%20approved%2C%20and%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20that%20branch%20feeling%20such%20a%20sense%20of%20accomplishment%2C%20because%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20saved%20my%20family%20from%20being%20jailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20just%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20over%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20week%20later%2C%20the%20scammers%20introduced%20new%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20a%20woman%20who%20had%20been%20scammed%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrime%20syndicate%26quot%3B%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20and%20that%20I%20was%20responsible%20for%20her%20death%20because%20she%20had%20transferred%20money%20into%20a%20bank%20account%20in%20my%20name.%20They%20told%20me%20the%20woman's%20son%20wanted%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20of%20my%20video%20calls%20with%20the%20police%20officer%2C%20I%20could%20hear%20the%20%26quot%3Bson%26quot%3B%20calling%20for%20justice%20for%20his%20mom.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20pay%20%24120%2C000%20in%20compensation%20for%20her%20death.%20The%20scammers%20acted%20like%20they%20helped%20me%20negotiate%20the%20amount%20down%20to%20%2460%2C000%2C%20which%20I%20got%20from%20my%20family%20through%20more%20lies%2C%20and%20wired%20it%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Binvestigation%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20ongoing%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half.%20I%20kept%20thinking%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20just%20want%20to%20be%20done%20with%20this.%20Why%20is%20it%20not%20over%20yet%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20report%20my%20whereabouts%20to%20them%20four%20times%20a%20day%20anymore%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20being%20monitored%20constantly%20both%20in%20my%20physical%20world%20and%20in%20the%20online%20world.%20I%20started%20to%20have%20suicidal%20ideation.%20I%20wanted%20to%20disappear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20scammers%20talked%20me%20out%20of%20those%20thoughts%2C%20telling%20me%20not%20to%20let%20the%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%26quot%3B%20win.%20Of%20course%2C%20now%20I%20realize%20they%20wouldn't%20let%20me%20die%20because%20they%20wanted%20me%20to%20keep%20wiring%20money%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EComing%20back%20to%20reality%2C%20my%20whole%20world%20came%20crashing%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scammers%20ultimately%20told%20me%20that%20the%20court%20thought%20the%20evidence%20I%20provided%20looked%20clean%2C%20but%20they%20needed%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20didn't%20keep%20any%20assets%20on%20my%20credit%20cards.%20On%20June%204%2C%20I%20was%20told%20to%20cash-advance%20them%20%2410%2C800%20from%20my%20three%20different%20credit%20cards%20and%20wire%20them%20all%20of%20the%20income%20I'd%20made%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months%20since%20the%20%26quot%3Binvestigation%26quot%3B%20had%20begun%2C%20totaling%20%2420%2C000.%20They%20told%20me%20this%20was%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20would%20present%20it%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%207%2C%20the%20fake%20officer%20sent%20me%20a%20text%20that%20the%20court%20had%20ruled%20me%20innocent%20and%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20need%20to%20give%20daily%20reports%20of%20my%20location%20and%20photos%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20I%20needed%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Thailand%20to%20collect%20repayment%20of%20the%20money%20I%20had%20sent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20looking%20up%20flight%20tickets.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20I%20sent%20him%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20potential%20flight%20option%20and%20called%20him%20multiple%20times%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20details%20of%20the%20security%20measures%20in%20place%2C%20because%20I%20was%20fearful%20about%20my%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20my%20phone%20calls%20went%20through%2C%20and%20that%20was%20when%20it%20hit%20me%3A%20They%20were%20gone%2C%20and%20my%20money%20was%20probably%20gone%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2011%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20FBI%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20asked%20the%20agents%20for%20a%20reality%20check.%20They%20said%20they%20ran%20my%20record%2C%20and%20it%20was%20clean.%20An%20FBI%20agent%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BYou've%20been%20scammed.%20You%20should%20report%20it%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20back%20to%20my%20office%20and%20sat%20in%20my%20chair%20looking%20up%20at%20the%20ceiling%2C%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20what%20the%20FBI%20agent%20said%20was%20real.%20Maybe%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20it%20was%20such%20a%20top-secret%20case%20that%20this%20FBI%20agent%20didn't%20know%20about%20it.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20discern%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20home%20and%20told%20the%20story%20to%20two%20friends%2C%20then%20called%20the%20Central%20Investigation%20Bureau%20(CIB)%20and%20a%20few%20other%20Thai%20organizations.%20They%20all%20told%20me%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20I'd%20been%20scammed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20my%20world%20came%20crashing%20down.%20I%20remember%20dropping%20onto%20the%20ground%20of%20my%20friends'%20apartment%20as%20the%20realization%20washed%20over%20me.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20painful%20moments%20of%20my%20life%20%E2%80%94%20coming%20to%20the%20realization%20that%20I%20had%20lost%20more%20than%20%24300%2C000.%20The%20money%20was%20gone.%20And%20not%20just%20my%20money%2C%20but%20also%20my%20family's%20money%20%E2%80%94%20pretty%20much%20my%20aunt's%20entire%20retirement%20fund.%20It%20was%20all%20because%20of%20me.%20The%20guilt%20will%20stay%20with%20me%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20friends%20and%20family%20have%20helped%20me%20through%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friends%20helped%20pick%20me%20up%20off%20the%20floor%20and%20make%20a%20step-by-step%20plan%2C%20including%20going%20to%20the%20banks%20to%20report%20fraudulent%20activity%2C%20filing%20a%20report%20with%20the%20FBI%20and%20the%20San%20Francisco%20police%2C%20and%20contacting%20the%20Thai%20embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20few%20days%20to%20call%20my%20brother%20and%20tell%20him%20what%20was%20going%20on.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20money%20you%20wired%20to%20me%20is%20gone%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20because%20of%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20my%20brother%20and%20my%20aunt%20called%20me%20together%20and%20asked%20what%20help%20I%20needed%2C%20and%20offered%20to%20fly%20to%20me%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20I'm%20very%20lucky%20that%20they%20are%20supportive.%20I'm%20sure%20that%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20that%20they're%20not%20asking%20me%20yet%2C%20but%20their%20main%20concern%20right%20now%20is%20my%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20remember%20something%20my%20brother%20said%20to%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20lose%20anything%20in%20this%20world%2C%20but%20you%20cannot%20lose%20yourself.%20You%20still%20have%20your%20brain%2C%20your%20legs.%20I'm%20glad%20that%20nothing%20bad%20happened%20to%20you.%20You%20still%20have%20your%20full%20potential%20and%20capability%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20that%20you%20do%2C%20to%20be%20you%2C%20and%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20on%20this%20world.%20You%20still%20have%20that%2C%20and%20know%20that%20that's%20something%20no%20one%20can%20take%20away%20from%20you.%26quot%3B%20I%20hold%20onto%20that%20%E2%80%94%20focusing%20on%20what%20I%20have%20and%20not%20on%20what%20I%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20doing%20better%20but%20still%20sometimes%20have%20nightmares%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20lost%20myself%20in%20those%20three%20months%3B%20it%20was%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20cult.%20All%20the%20lies%20and%20threats%20prevented%20me%20from%20taking%20the%20steps%20I%20should've%20taken%20to%20protect%20myself.%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20the%20scammer%20because%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felderly-immigrant-parents-lost-life-savings-investment-scam-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escammed%20my%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20by%20lying%20to%20them.%20It%20broke%20my%20heart%20and%20I'm%20disgusted%20with%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20week%20is%20better%2C%20but%20there%20are%20nights%20I%20still%20have%20nightmares%2C%20and%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20crying.%20I%20spiral%20into%