tunity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall-cap%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lagging%20large-caps%20for%20the%20last%20year%2C%20small-caps%20have%20rallied%20over%20the%20last%20several%20weeks.%20While%20some%20market%20experts%20see%20this%20as%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20small-cap%20revival%2C%20a%20growing%20chorus%20of%20strategists%20believe%20the%20trade%20doesn't%20have%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERate%20cuts%20could%20help%20small-caps%2C%20which%20typically%20carry%20more%20debt%20on%20their%20balance%20sheets%20than%20their%20larger%20counterparts%20and%20would%20experience%20more%20debt%20relief%20and%20earnings%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20rate%20cuts%20may%20not%20override%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20entering%20a%20period%20of%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-pullback-correction-slowing-economy-buy-the-dip-lpl-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeffrey%20Buchbinder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20LPL%20Financial's%20chief%20equity%20strategist%2C%20believes%20that%20while%20small-cap%20underperformance%20makes%20valuations%20attractive%2C%20a%20slowing%20economy%20is%20not%20the%20ideal%20part%20of%20the%20business%20cycle%20for%20small-caps%20to%20outperform.%20In%20his%20opinion%2C%20the%20best%20time%20to%20buy%20small-caps%20is%20when%20the%20economy%20enters%20a%20period%20of%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafe-quality-dividend-stocks-buy-cooling-economy-volatilitiy-recession-risk-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChad%20Oviatt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20director%20of%20investment%20management%20at%20Huntington%20Private%20Bank%2C%20echoes%20this%20sentiment.%20According%20to%20Oviatt%2C%20there%20are%20certainly%20promising%20individual%20small-cap%20investments.%20However%2C%20performance%20in%20this%20area%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20ultimately%20tied%20to%20the%20health%20of%20the%20overall%20US%20economy%2C%20as%20many%20small-cap%20companies%20are%20highly%20sensitive%20to%20economic%20cycles.%20The%20US%20dollar%20has%20also%20come%20under%20pressure%20recently.%20Oviatt%20believes%20a%20lower%20dollar%20could%20result%20in%20more%20favorable%20US%20export%20numbers%2C%20which%20he%20thinks%20will%20boost%20larger%20companies%20more%20than%20smaller%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rotation%20out%20of%20Big%20Tech%20isn't%20sufficient%20to%20save%20small-caps%20either%2C%20according%20to%20Clyde%20Rossouw%2C%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20asset%20management%20firm%20Ninety%20One.%20He%20doesn't%20think%20it's%20reasonable%20to%20believe%20investors%20are%20taking%20their%20money%20from%20Big%20Tech%20and%20funneling%20it%20into%20small-caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20difficult%20to%20see%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20money%20going%20into%20small-caps%20by%20definition%20because%20the%20actual%20investible%20opportunity%20is%20so%20little%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rossouw.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20%242%20trillion%20came%20out%20of%20Microsoft%20hypothetically.%20It%20couldn't%20go%20into%20the%20Russell%202000.%20There's%20not%20enough%20stocks%20to%20buy%20and%20it%20could%20almost%20cause%20a%20market%20distortion.%26quot%3B%20In%20his%20opinion%2C%20a%20sustained%20flow%20of%20money%20from%20Big%20Tech%20to%20small-cap%20isn't%20a%20realistic%20expectation%2C%20so%20don't%20count%20on%20the%20market%20rotation%20to%20boost%20the%20small-cap%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERossouw%20also%20points%20out%20that%20while%20rate%20cuts%20certainly%20will%20help%20small-caps%2C%20their%20performance%20is%20overly%20dependent%20on%20the%20Fed's%20actions.%20If%20the%20Fed%20doesn't%20cut%20rates%20as%20quickly%20as%20markets%20expect%2C%20then%20the%20earnings%20risk%20for%20small-caps%20will%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20macroeconomic%20situation%2C%20small-cap%20earnings%20simply%20haven't%20kept%20up%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%20This%20creates%20a%20glaring%20disparity%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20strong%20performance%20of%20large-caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuidance%20has%20been%20weak%20(vs.%20surprisingly%20strong%20in%20large%20caps)%2C%20sales%20have%20missed%2C%20revisions%20are%20negative%2C%20and%20the%20profits%20recovery%20has%20once%20again%20been%20pushed%20out%20another%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Jill%20Hall%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20head%20of%20US%20small%20and%20mid-cap%20strategy%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%20The%20financial%20reality%20for%20small-caps%20hasn't%20been%20the%20most%20optimistic%20coming%20out%20of%20second-quarter%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d40bf88e-6adb-4e47-8725-51ee38b69870%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvest%20in%20quality%20instead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20investment%20for%20a%20cooling%20economy%20is%20to%20seek%20out%20quality%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20believes%20volatility%20will%20be%20the%20new%20normal%20for%20markets%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20companies%20with%20resilient%20business%20models%20and%20strong%20financial%20metrics%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20weather%20choppier%20economic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuality%20has%20been%20the%20most%20consistent%20leader%20in%20downturns%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20this%20perspective%2C%20the%20small-cap%20trade%20doesn't%20seem%20quite%20as%20hot%2C%20as%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20Russell%202000%20stocks%20are%20unprofitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20you%20should%20write%20off%20small-caps%20completely%2C%20but%20investors%20who%20are%20still%20interested%20in%20buying%20small-caps%20should%20do%20so%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20quality%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERossouw%20concurs%20with%20this%20quality-first%20approach%2C%