lage%2C%20he%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20police%20service.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20join%20a%20coaching%20centre%20but%20the%20fee%20for%20the%20course%20was%20Rs%203%2C000.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20so%20I%20started%20selling%20tea%20at%20a%20small%20shop.%20I%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%20and%20collected%20the%20amount%20to%20afford%20the%20fee.%20It%20was%20humble%20of%20the%20teacher%20to%20waive%20off%20my%20fee%20when%20he%20came%20to%20know%20about%20my%20financial%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Amit%20secured%20a%20job%20as%20a%20constable%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318386%2Fdelhi-police-constable-than-singh-runs-free-school-for-slum-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20posted%20in%20Rohini%20district%20on%20the%20mobile%20crime%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amit%20prepares%20students%20for%20competitive%20exams%20like%20SSC%20CGL%2C%20Haryana%20Staff%20Selection%20Commission%2C%20and%20more.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Famit-lathia-1724916499-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20c