ra%20months%20before%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20condemned%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20and%20given%20the%20call%20for%20a%20silent%20protest%20to%20demand%20action%20against%20those%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20painful%20and%20heart-wrenching%20that%20the%20statue%20of%20the%20great%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20erected%20at%20the%20Rajkot%20fort%20in%20Malvan%20has%20crashed.%20It%20is%20shocking%20that%20this%20statue%20fell%20in%20just%20eight%20months%20(after%20it%20was%20inaugurated)%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20NCP%20president%20Sunil%20Tatkare%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20an%20unforgivable%20mistake%20was%20made.%20In%20order%20to%20protest%20this%20tragedy%20and%20to%20take%20precautions%20to%20prevent%20such%20accidents%20from%20happening%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20has%20organized%20a%20rally%20across%20the%20state%20on%20Thursday%2C%20dt.%20On%2029%20August%202024%20from%2011%3A00%20am%20to%2012%3A00%20pm%2C%20we%20will%20hold%20a%20silent%20protest%20in%20front%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20statue.%20We%20will%20demand%20that%20strict%20action%20be%20taken%20against%20whoever%20is%20guilty%20in%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20demanded%20that%20the%20government%20work%20round%20the%20clock%20and%20build%20a%20new%20statue%20at%20Rajkot%20Fort%20to%20honour%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2035-foot%20statue%20of%20the%2017th%20century%20ruler%20was%20unveiled%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statue's%20collapse%20on%20Monday%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20of%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%20demanding%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20resignation.%20A%20complaint%20by%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20alleged%20that%20construction%20of%20the%20statue%20was%20not%20up%20to%20the%20mark%20and%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20used%20in%20the%20structure%20were%20rusted.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20two%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20project%20--%20contractor%20Jaydeep%20Apte%20and%20structural%20consultant%20Chetan%20Patil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20to%20hold%20a%20silent%20protest%20against%20the%20government%20he%20is%20part%20of%20needs%20to%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20current%20political%20landscape%20in%20Maharashtra.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20sea%20of%20change%20in%20the%20state's%20political%20equations%20between%20last%20election%20and%20this%20one.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20split%20into%20the%20factions%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20into%20factions%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recently%20held%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20put%20up%20a%20stellar%20show%2C%20winning%2030%20out%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20will%20now%20be%20looking%20to%20repeat%20the%20strong%20performance%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%20The%20BJP-led%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20go%20all%20out%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20the%20backdrop%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20decision%20to%20call%20a%20protest%20is%20politically%20significant.%20His%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20lost%20several%20leaders%20to%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20after%20the%20poll%20results.%20He%20also%20admitted%20that%20fielding%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20against%20his%20cousin%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmistake%26quot%3B.%20The%20developments%20have%20sparked%20buzz%20on%20whether%20the%20junior%20Pawar%20is%20considering%20returning%20to%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20camp%20after%20a%20string%20of%20setbacks.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20is%20firmly%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20bloc%20will%20form%20the%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724908500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ftjo5u46g_ajit-pawar_625x300_19_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawars-ncp-to-lead-silent-protest-over-shivaji-statue-collapse-6442360%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20signs%20of%20rumblings%20within%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20in%20Maharashtra%20months%20before%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20condemned%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20and%20given%20the%20call%20for%20a%20silent%20protest%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawars-ncp-to-lead-silent-protest-over-shivaji-statue-collapse-6442360%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana%20on%20the%20time%20'200%20FIRs'%20were%20filed%20against%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724907914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112885104%2Cimgsize-35218.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-kangana-ranaut-reflected-on-the-time-when-200-firs-were-filed-against-her-daily%2Farticleshow%2F112885002.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112885002.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBoll