s)%20and%20disability%20quota%20benefits%2C%20has%20told%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20that%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20-%20which%20conducts%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20-%20has%20no%20power%20to%20take%20disqualify%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcentre-allows-upsc-to-perform-aadhaar-based-authentication-for-candidates-verifications-6441616%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20cancelled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fias-officer-puja-khedkar-upsc-changed-her-name-also-parents-names-upsc-on-how-puja-khedkar-cheated-6231015%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuja%20Khedkar's%20candidature%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20debarred%20her%20from%20future%20exams.%20The%20Commission%20alleged%20that%20she%20misrepresented%20information%20in%20her%20application%20for%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%2C%202022%20to%20get%20reservation%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20selected%20and%20appointed%20as%20a%20Probationary%20Officer%2C%20UPSC%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20disqualify%20the%20candidature%2C%26quot%3B%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20anticipatory%20bail%20in%20the%20criminal%20case%20against%20her%2C%20said%20in%20a%20response%20filed%20before%20the%20court%20on%20the%20UPSC's%20charges%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20now%20only%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20can%20take%20action%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPuja%20Khedkar%20On%20UPSC's%20%26quot%3BChanged%20Her%20Name%26quot%3B%20Charge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20has%20claimed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-against-puja-khedkars-father-for-obstructing-government-work-6298888%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuja%20Khedkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20attempted%20the%20uber-competitive%20qualifying%20test%20more%20than%20the%20six%20times%20permitted%20for%20a%20general%20category%20candidate.%20She%20did%20so%20by%20changing%20her%20name%2C%20and%20that%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Commission%20said%20it%20could%20not%20detect%20the%20violation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuja%20Khedkar%2C%20however%2C%20refuted%20these%20allegations%20and%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20in%20her%20name%20or%20surname%20from%202012%20to%202022.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20given%20any%20wrong%20information%20about%20herself%20to%20the%20UPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUPSC%20verified%20my%20identity%20through%20biometric%20data.%20The%20Commission%20did%20not%20find%20my%20documents%20fake%20or%20incorrect.%20My%20educational%20certificate%2C%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20other%20personal%20information%20were%20found%20to%20be%20absolutely%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20necessary%20verifications%20were%20also%20done%20by%20DoPT.%20As%20per%20DoPT%2C%20a%20medical%20board%20constituted%20by%20AIIMS%20conducted%20my%20medical%20examination.%20The%20board%20found%20my%20disability%20to%20be%20up%20to%2047%25%20and%20more%20than%20the%2040%25%20disability%20required%20for%20the%20PwBD%20(Person%20with%20Benchmark%20Disability)%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPuja%20Khedkar's%20%26quot%3BFraud%26quot%3B%20Not%20Only%20Against%20Us%20But%20Public%20Too%3A%20UPSC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20opposed%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20an%20anticipatory%20bail%20petition%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkars-fraud-not-only-against-us-but-public-too-upsc-to-court-6388129%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuja%20Khedkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20she%20committed%20%26quot%3Bfraud%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20commission%20and%20the%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20reply%20filed%20in%20court%20on%20August%2021%2C%20the%20UPSC%20said%20Puja%20Khedkar's%20custodial%20interrogation%20was%20necessary%20to%20unearth%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfraud%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20not%20have%20been%20done%20without%20the%20help%20of%20other%20individuals.%20Therefore%2C%20her%20pre-arrest%20bail%20plea%20should%20be%20dismissed%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gravity%20of%20the%20fraud%20committed%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20nature%20having%20been%20committed%20against%20not%20only%20a%20constitutional%20body%20--%20the%20complainant%20--%20whose%20traditions%20are%20untrammelled%20and%20unparalleled%20but%20also%20against%20the%20public%20at%20large%2C%20including%20the%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20who%20have%20utmost%20faith%20upon%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20UPSC%20as%20well%20as%20persons%20who%20could%20not%20be%20appointed%20despite%20being%20duly%20eligible%20and%20qualified%20due%20to%20illegal%20means%20employed%20by%20the%20applicant%20to%20seek%20appointment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UPSC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20also%20sought%20dismissal%20of%20the%20pre-arrest%20bail%20plea%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20any%20relief%20to%20her%20would%20hinder%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeep-rooted%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20case%20has%20wider%20implications%20on%20public%20trust%20as%20well%20as%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20will%20today%20hear%20her%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724907660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ffotfgccg_puja-khedkar-ias_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuja-khedkar-tells-delhi-high-court-upsc-has-no-power-to