etails%20for%20over%20Rs%2050%20lakh%2C%20were%20damaged%20by%20an%20overnight%20period%20of%20intense%20downpour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20left%20to%20live%20for%20anymore...All%20the%203%20cars%20mentioned%20in%20my%20flair%20are%20now%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20of%20the%20post%20alongside%20the%20images%20of%20the%20cars%20almost%20drowned%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCarsIndia%2Fcomments%2F1f27l1e%2Ftheres_nothing_left_to_live_for_anymore%2F%5C%22%3EThere's%20nothing%20left%20to%20live%20for%20anymore%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FLazy_Management_6206%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FLazy_Management_6206%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FCarsIndia%2F%5C%22%3ECarsIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20comments%20section%2C%20the%20user%20explained%20that%20there%20was%20up%20to%20eight%20feet%20water%20outside%20his%20house%20and%20nobody%20could%20come%20to%20tow%20the%20vehicles.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20the%203rd%20time%20I'm%20facing%20this.%20Twice%20in%20my%20previous%20society%20(with%20completely%20different%20cars)%20and%20the%20first%20time%20in%204%20years%20at%20this%20new%20place.%20Theres%207-8%20ft%20water%20outside%20no%20one%20can%20come%20in%20till%20the%20water%20goes%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20the%20water%20%26quot%3Bhas%20seeped%207%20inches%20by%20far%20now%20into%20my%20house%20and%20almost%204%20feet%20outside%20my%20house.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20area%20or%20the%20whole%20city%20has%20been%20affected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20a%20thousand%20reactions%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20we