s%20tapering%20away%20towards%20the%20river.%20Nothing%20was%20being%20retained%20in%20the%20land.%20The%20rain%20was%20taking%20away%20my%20topsoil%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20we%20created%20the%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20to%20ensure%20that%20rainwater%20recharges%20our%20land.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20magic%2C%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20they%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345145%2Fforest-officer-saves-trees-in-chhattisgarh-forest-tiger-reserve-from-encroachers-ifs-varun-jain-timber-poaching%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewilding%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20says%20that%20they%20took%20cues%20from%20the%20forest%20next%20door.%20They%20observed%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20species%20that%20grew%20there%20and%20worked%20on%20recreating%20the%20broken%20linkages%20between%20different%20species%20and%20creating%20an%20interdependence%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22how%20to%20build%20a%20biosphere%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F