0to%20predict%20Taliban%20attacks%20in%20Afghanistan.%20An%20Economist%20report%20states%20that%20the%20model%20had%20achieved%2070%25%20accuracy%20by%20October%202020.%20Since%20then%2C%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20across%20the%20world%20have%20turned%20to%20AI%20to%20help%20understand%20patterns%20and%20build%20indicators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20of%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20the%20state%20police%20force%20perform%20their%20duties%20more%20efficiently.%20This%20will%20be%20done%20through%20Maharashtra%20Research%20and%20Vigilance%20for%20Enhanced%20Law%20Enforcement%20(MARVEL)%2C%20a%20separate%20entity%2C%20created%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStated%20to%20be%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20country%2C%20this%20initiative%20is%20dedicated%20solely%20to%20the%20integration%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20into%20law%20enforcement.%20The%20entity%E2%80%99s%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20develop%20AI%20tools%20tailored%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20various%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20within%20the%20state.%20These%20tools%20are%20not%20just%20generic%20solutions%20but%20are%20tailor-made%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20requirements%20of%20different%20police%20departments.%20They%20will%20improve%20crime%20prediction%20and%20enable%20speedy%20resolution%20of%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%20will%20be%20used%20for%20various%20critical%20applications%20%E2%80%93%20from%20missing%20persons%2C%20hit%20and%20runs%20to%20organised%20crime%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESujata%20Saunik%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20states%20that%20the%20mission%20is%20to%20use%20the%20latest%20AI%20tools%20on%20crime%20data%20to%20speed%20up%20investigations%2C%20leading%20to%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20how%20this%20AI%20tool%20can%20possibly%20change%20the%20way%20cases%20are%20handled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%20humans%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%20is%20a%20Special%20Purpose%20Vehicle%20(SPV)%2C%20formed%20through%20a%20tripartite%20agreement%20between%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)-Nagpur%20and%20Pinaka%20Technologies%20Private%20Limited.%20It%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarssh%20Poddar%2C%20SP%20of%20Nagpur%20Rural%20and%20ex-officio%20Director%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20MARVEL%20spoke%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20about%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201542px)%20100vw%2C%201542px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harssh%20Poddar%2C%20SP%20of%20Nagpur%20Rural%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%201542w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%