s%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20rural%20SP%20states%20that%20the%20role%20of%20AI%20can%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAI%20might%20notice%20details%20in%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20that%20a%20human%20might%20miss%2C%20such%20as%20the%20specific%20make%20of%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20it%20travels%2C%20or%20the%20type%20of%20helmet%20used%20by%20the%20perpetrator.%20These%20subtle%20patterns%20can%20be%20crucial%20in%20solving%20cases%20and%20preventing%20future%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20states%20too%20might%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20augment%20law%20enforcement%2C%20Maharashtra%20might%20be%20the%20first%20to%20create%20an%20independent%20entity%20for%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20role%20of%20MARVEL%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20solutions%20on%20a%20case%20to%20case%20basis.%20Instead%2C%20it%20focuses%20on%20developing%20tools%20and%20algorithms%20that%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20can%20deploy%20in%20their%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284171%2Fpolice-inspector-teaches-poor-children-ayodhya-inspiration-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagpur%20Rural%20SP%20%3C%2Fa%3Estates%20that%20if%20a%20particular%20police%20team%20wants%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20deal%20with%20cases%20of%20missing%20people%2C%20and%20share%20their%20requirements%2C%20MARVEL%20would%20design%20it%20and%20share%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20an%20investigative%20agency%20that%20is%20providing%20help%20with%20particular%20cases.%20We%20would%20design%20a%20tool%20depending%20upon%20the%20requirement%20of%20the%20other%20agency%20and%20then%20we%20would%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20stresses%20Harrsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20can%20solve%20complex%20crimes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20MARVEL%20is%20working%20on%20five%20different%20projects%20for%20as%20many%20agencies.%20It%20has%2025%20technical%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20AI%20tools%20will%20be%20able%20to%20layer%20data%20and%20give%20a%20fair%20sense%20of%20what%20might%20have%20happened.%20It%20would%20give%20predictive%20modelling%20solutions%2C%20which%20officials%20will%20then%20have%20to%20interpret.%20It%20will%20show%20you%20trends%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Sujata%20Saunik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362910%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20major%20use%20cases%20would%20include%20missing%20women%20and%20children%20cases%2C%20where%20AI%20algorithms%20are%20already%20being%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDistricts%20like%20Nagpur%20have%20CCTV%20cameras%20under%20smart%20city%20projects%2C%20thanks%20to%20which%2C%20large%20volumes%20of%20visual%20data%20can%20be%20analysed%20rapidly.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20get%20the%20metadata%20of%20large%20volumes%20of%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20you%20can%20have%20any%20AI%20algorithm%20that%20is%20able%20to%20go%20through%20it%20in%20order%20to%20detect%20a%20person%20that%20you%20are%20looking%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO%20of%20MARVEL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20other%20examples%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20this%20tool%20would%20be%20very%20useful%20in%20accidental%20deaths%2C%20hit%20and%20run%20cases.%20Even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362304%2Fwalkfit-ai-walking-stick-fall-prevention-osteoarthritis-osteoporosis-seniors-elderly-rahi-shah-hriday-boriawala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspect%20vehicles%20can%20be%20found%20through%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20scanning%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20toll%20plazas%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20AI%20algorithm%20can%20actually%20make%20a%20calculation%20for%20you%20to%20be%20able%20to%20say%20which%20vehicles%20would%20have%20passed%20at%20the%20point%20of%20accident%20at%20this%20speed.%20This%20would%20essentially%20narrow%20down%20the%20suspect%20list%20to%20four%20or%20five%20vehicles%2C%20making%20investigation%20easier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20area%20where%20AI%20will%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20is%20in%20organised%20crime%20cases%20like%20narcotics%2C%20human%20trafficking%2C%20wildlife%20trade.%20These%20cases%20come%20with%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20across%20several%20years%2C%20including%20financial%20transactions%2C%20communication%20records%2C%20and%20surveillance%20footage.%20AI%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20perform%20relationship%20mapping%20and%20pattern%20recognition%20makes%20it%20an%20invaluable%20tool%20in%20these%20complex%20investigations%2C%20explains%20Harssh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20can%20process%20and%20analyse%20data%20at%20scales%20beyond%20human%20capability%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages.%20The%20more%20data%20AI%20algorithms%20are%20exposed%20to%2C%20the%20more%20refined%20and%20accurate%20they%20become%2C%20just%20like%20Raven%20Sentry%20proved.%20Initially%2C%20while%20the%20predictions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20correct%2C%20as%20and%20when%20the%20data%20increased%2C%20it%20predicted%20an%20attack%20in%20Jalalabad%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20occurred%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20perfect%20these%20algorithms%20over%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20can%20eventually%20provide%20near-flawless%20support%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20technology%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20MARVEL%E2%80%99s%20work%20today%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20and%20human%20expertise%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fscience-and-technology%2F2024%2F07%2F31%2Fhow-america-built-an-ai-tool-to-predict-taliban-attacks%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20America%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20predict%20Taliban%20attacks%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20on%2031%20July%202024%2C%20Courtesy%20The%20Economist%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724680016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20government's%20MARVEL%20will%20augment%20law%20enforcement%20by%20developing%20AI%20tools%20to%20provide%20tailor-made%20solutions%20to%20the%20police%20force