toms.%20They%20responded%20saying%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20fungal%20infection%20and%20that%20I%20should%20resort%20to%20a%20particular%20chemical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20like%20these%2C%20when%20Deka%20responds%20by%20saying%20he%20does%20not%20use%20chemicals%20on%20his%20plants%2C%20the%20line%20remains%20silent%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20This%20journey%20of%20odds%20would%20deter%20him%20you%E2%80%99d%20think.%20But%20it%20only%20makes%20him%20more%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500-plus%20trees%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20Medini%20Homestay%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Indian%20olive%2C%20guava%2C%20mango%2C%20papaya%2C%20and%20banana%20%E2%80%94%20sway%20in%20the%20breeze%2C%20almost%20bowing%20down%20to%20him%20in%20thanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20passion%20project%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20wood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20around%20the%20Medini%20Homestay%20is%20filled%20with%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20glistening%20water%20droplets%20at%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20leaves%20refracting%20the%20light%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20featuring%20the%20entire%20forest%20in%20a%20single%20drop.%20The%20view%20from%20your%20room%20is%20glorious.%20A%20drone%20view%20of%20the%20property%20reveals%20two%20blocks%20of%20construction.%20As%20Meynell%20explains%2C%20these%20are%20the%20family%20block%20and%20the%20guest%20block.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20both%20identical%20and%20each%20has%20four%20rooms.%20The%20maximum%20capacity%20of%20the%20guest%20block%20is%20to%20accommodate%20nine%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20s