er%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoonfuls%20of%20knowledge%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20his%20open%20air%20classes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumna%20of%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20in%20Santikentan%2C%20he%20imbibed%20the%20principles%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20by%20providing%20a%20holistic%20education%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%2C%20which%20goes%20beyond%20merely%20words%20written%20in%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20five%20children%20in%202021%2C%20today%20over%20105%20children%20study%20at%20Angshuman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%E2%80%99%20(Anirvana%20means%20inextinguishable%20and%20Gach%20means%20tree).%20Running%20on%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20his%20own%20savings%2C%20it%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20month%20to%20educate%20a%20child%20in%20this%20school%20under%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngshuman%20works%20as%20a%20Bengali%20literature%20professor%20at%20Prof%20Syed%20Nurul%20Hasan%20College%20in%20Farakka%2C%20Murshidabad.%20Raised%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%20and%20inspired%20by%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20teachings%2C%20he%20pursued%20his%20higher%20studies%20at%20Visva%20Bharati%20university.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20is%20held%20in%20the%20open%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgacher-skul-min-1724074337-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20is%20held%20in%20the%20open%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENature%20had%20always%20been%20his%20friend%20and%20supported%20him%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20While%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20personally%20in%202019%2C%20the%20teacher%20sought%20solace%20in%20nature%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20gradually%20reducing.%20I%20was%20depressed%20and%20wished%20to%20utilise%20my%20time%20in%20a%20productive%20manner%20post%20work.%20I%20put%20out%20a%20Facebook%20post%20in%202019%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20plant%20saplings%20and%20people%20were%20welcome%20to%20join%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angshuman%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive%20and%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%20whose%20first%20agenda%20was%20planting%2050%20saplings%20on%205%20June%202019.%20Being%20on%20the%20ground%20led%20to%20several%20interactions%20with%20locals%20and%20students.%20The%20teacher%20took%20some%20of%20them%20under%20his%20wings%20and%20would%20solve%20their%20doubts%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20former%20students%20hailed%20from%20a%20village%20called%20Samlapur%20in%20Farakka%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20visit%20their%20village.%20It%20was%20after%20the%20first%20lockdown%20that%20the%20teacher%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20and%20he%20was%20astonished%20by%20what%20he%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20setting%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329929%2Farchana-nooguri-headmistress-government-school-national-teachers-award-enrollment-dropout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20matched%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20beautiful%20and%20lush%20green.%20I%20had%20been%20meaning%20to%20start%20a%20school%20for%20children%2C%20and%20seeing%20the%20village%20and%20its%20children%20gave%20me%20the%20push%20I%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20financial%20backing%2C%20constructing%20four%20walls%20for%20a%20school%20was%20also%20not%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tribal%20hamlet%2C%20Samlapur%20housed%20first%20generation%20learners%2C%20who%20were%20severely%20affected%20by%20schools%20shutting%20down.%20Their%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20daily%20wage%20workers%2C%20had%20no%20work%20and%20their%20worsening%20economic%20situations%20forced%20the%20children%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudents%20were%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20mid-day%20meals.%20The%20students%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Adivasi%20families%20are%20extremely%20marginalised.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20continue%20their%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Farakka%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%2C%20an%20open%20air%20school%20under%20the%20shades%20of%20trees%20was%20born%20in%202021%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20school%20to%20these%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Fut